citations:
    citation-affc-cersei-vi:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Cersei VI"
            text_from_source: "Septa Moelle was a white-haired harridan with a face as sharp as an axe and lips pursed in perpetual disapproval."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Septa Moelle arrives at court announcing that Margaery and her cousins (Megga and Elinor Tyrell) have been arrested by the Faith. Osney Kettleblack's confession of adultery with the queen has been accepted by the High Septon. Grand Maester Pycelle confirms he provided Margaery moon tea. Cersei issues blank arrest warrants for Margaery's supposed lovers (Ser Tallad, Jalabhar Xho, Hugh Clifton, Hamish the Harper, Mark Mullendore, Lambert Turnberry, Bayard Norcross, and the Redwyne twins). She makes Orton Merryweather Hand of the King and sends Aurane Waters and his dromonds to guard the Blackwater."
